attributes.review:
I downloaded this app because I support trump ✨💕 once opened the app glitched.A day passed  and my family got sick. We went to the hospital and they didn’t give us answers.And no we didn’t have the rona❌🦠, anyways 2 days passed and we got worse and worse.I told my neighbor to check on my fish because we left him alone she told us that my fish died I was so devastated i’m pretty sure it was this app 😡 My dog was also a huge fan of trump my neighbor said that he ran away 😢 The doctor said if one of us had downloaded the trump app and I said “Yes I have” so he told me to erase it so I did and we all got better ☺️  DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS !!!! 
Also BLM  and MLM.
